{"about_the_game":"ParaPerspective is a puzzle game where moving the camera affects the state of the world, by rotating it around you can create geometrically impossible connections.<br><br>When you align blocks, slopes and stairs to make them <strong>appear</strong> connected, they <strong>become</strong> connected. Even gravity itself is affected, making you fall on what <strong>seems</strong> to be below you. The game is divided in worlds that provide you with loads of bite-sized puzzles that you can solve at your own pace. Skip to the next one if you can't figure this one out, and come back later!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make your own levels</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/extras/steam_level_editor.png?t=1710778557\" /><br>With the in-game editor, you can easily make and share levels! It's simple and intuitive, the levels can be shared with your friends as a string of text or as png card, just like the one below!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/extras/steam_level.png?t=1710778557\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1710778557","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1710778557","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1710778557","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1710778557","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"ParaPerspective is a puzzle game where moving the camera affects the state of the world, by rotating it around you 